  "detailed_description": "Welcome to ArkCraft: The Rebirth of the World<br><br>Experience a unique crafting and building game that takes you on an epic journey through antiquity. Take on the role of a pioneer in a world threatened by an impending flood, and build the legendary Ark to save humanity and the animal kingdom.<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/31890117bd55a755325007a4f55a0a32.poster.avif?t=1773466645\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/31890117bd55a755325007a4f55a0a32.webm?t=1773466645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/31890117bd55a755325007a4f55a0a32.mp4?t=1773466645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>FEATURES:<br><br>Build the Ark of your dreams: Utilize your crafting skills to construct the Ark and populate it with a variety of animals and plants. Customize your Ark to your liking and create a home for yourself and your community.<br><br>Explore a vibrant world: Immerse yourself in a rich and dynamic world full of adventure and discovery. Explore different biomes, from dense forests to rugged mountains, and encounter a variety of wild animals and mysterious ruins.<br><br>Survive and thrive: Master the art of survival as you face the challenges of a changing world. Gather resources, craft tools and weapons, and learn to defend yourself against wild animals and natural disasters.<br><br>Research and evolve: Unlock new skills and technologies as you track your progress through Skill Trees and Tech Trees. Discover new agricultural and crafting techniques, upgrade your equipment to survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/41f22b145c1e757fac50714d3ee7e0c2.poster.avif?t=1773466645\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/41f22b145c1e757fac50714d3ee7e0c2.webm?t=1773466645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/41f22b145c1e757fac50714d3ee7e0c2.mp4?t=1773466645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build a completely new settlement after the flood to give mankind hope again. Protect your subjects against harsh conditions and mysterious creatures. <br><br>Are you ready to take on the challenge and reshape the world? Join the ArkCraft community today and become part of an epic adventure.",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to ArkCraft: The Rebirth of the World<br><br>Experience a unique crafting and building game that takes you on an epic journey through antiquity. Take on the role of a pioneer in a world threatened by an impending flood, and build the legendary Ark to save humanity and the animal kingdom.<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/31890117bd55a755325007a4f55a0a32.poster.avif?t=1773466645\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/31890117bd55a755325007a4f55a0a32.webm?t=1773466645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/31890117bd55a755325007a4f55a0a32.mp4?t=1773466645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>FEATURES:<br><br>Build the Ark of your dreams: Utilize your crafting skills to construct the Ark and populate it with a variety of animals and plants. Customize your Ark to your liking and create a home for yourself and your community.<br><br>Explore a vibrant world: Immerse yourself in a rich and dynamic world full of adventure and discovery. Explore different biomes, from dense forests to rugged mountains, and encounter a variety of wild animals and mysterious ruins.<br><br>Survive and thrive: Master the art of survival as you face the challenges of a changing world. Gather resources, craft tools and weapons, and learn to defend yourself against wild animals and natural disasters.<br><br>Research and evolve: Unlock new skills and technologies as you track your progress through Skill Trees and Tech Trees. Discover new agricultural and crafting techniques, upgrade your equipment to survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/41f22b145c1e757fac50714d3ee7e0c2.poster.avif?t=1773466645\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/41f22b145c1e757fac50714d3ee7e0c2.webm?t=1773466645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869610/extras/41f22b145c1e757fac50714d3ee7e0c2.mp4?t=1773466645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build a completely new settlement after the flood to give mankind hope again. Protect your subjects against harsh conditions and mysterious creatures. <br><br>Are you ready to take on the challenge and reshape the world? Join the ArkCraft community today and become part of an epic adventure.",
